            <h1>Mandela Day 2014</h1>
            <h3>July 18th, Los Angeles</h3>

            <p>Legacy of Hope hosted dignitaries, celebrities and advocates at the Beverly Hills Wallis Annenberg Center for the Performing Arts, to celebrate the life and Legacy of Nelson Mandela. During this event held on Mandela Day (July 18th), the Legacy of Hope announced plans for a worldwide simulcast concert scheduled to take place in New York on December 13th, 2014. <a href="/concert">This concert</a>, to be held at the Barclay Center, NY, will support the ongoing campaign by Legacy of Hope to raise funds for the Nelson Mandela Children’s Hospital, slated to open in 2016.</p>

